PROGRAM-2-CREATE VARIABLE OF EACH DATA TYPE AND PRINT THEIR TYPES USING type()

CODE-
#Variable of different data type
integer_num = 10      
float_num = 3.14
is_true = True
text = "Vandana"
#Print values and their type
print(integer_num, type(integer_num))
print(float_num, type(float_num))
print(is_true, type(is_true))
print(text, type(text))

OUTPUT-
10 <class 'int'>
3.14 <class 'float'>
True <class 'bool'>
Vandana <class 'str'>
